            <h2>PEN/GEOS</h2>
            <p>PEN/GEOS 1.0 was the new name for PC/GEOS 2.0 when GeoWorks released it on 9 April 1992.</p>
            <p>PEN/GEOS 2.0 was released in 1992, and version 3.0 was released in 1995.</p>

            <h3>Nokia Communicator 9000(i) and 9110(i)</h3>
            <p>In 1996, the <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Nokia 9000 Communicator', 'ITH'); ?> smartphone was introduced.</p>
            <p>This phone uses PEN/GEOS 3.0 and established the smartphone market.</p>
